Go on.

566
00:41:01,766 --> 00:41:03,167
I'll take care of things here.

567
00:41:03,810 --> 00:41:04,744
Thanks, Brother.

568
00:41:05,810 --> 00:41:07,720
I'm hungry, so I'll start eating first.

569
00:41:08,217 --> 00:41:09,551
But if I get sleepy...

570
00:41:10,094 --> 00:41:11,716
I'll wait for you here and sleep.

571
00:41:12,044 --> 00:41:12,837
That's so perfect.

572
00:41:13,425 --> 00:41:14,762
I love a man like that.

573
00:41:15,079 --> 00:41:17,274
Eats when he's hungry, sleeps when he's tired.

574
00:41:17,274 --> 00:41:18,690
Killing it, sis!

575
00:41:18,690 --> 00:41:19,744
I'll be back.

576
00:41:31,310 --> 00:41:31,810
Yeah?

577
00:41:31,810 --> 00:41:33,277
Erng, where the hell are you?

578
00:41:33,510 --> 00:41:35,277
In the deepest level of hell. It's so hot.

579
00:41:36,044 --> 00:41:37,944
Seriously, you've arrived, right?

580
00:41:38,310 --> 00:41:39,110
I'm here.

581
00:41:39,644 --> 00:41:41,077
You haven't just been sleeping, have you?

582
00:41:41,710 --> 00:41:42,330
I haven't been sleeping.

583
00:41:42,330 --> 00:41:44,810
I even woke up early to go to the temple
and pray for a boyfriend.

584
00:41:45,044 --> 00:41:46,244
So, did you get one?

585
00:41:46,444 --> 00:41:47,244
Jeez.

586
00:41:47,444 --> 00:41:48,632
It's not going to happen that fast.

587
00:41:49,084 --> 00:41:50,274
So, why are you calling? Is it urgent?

588
00:41:51,110 --> 00:41:53,067
I was just calling to check if you went.

589
00:41:53,067 --> 00:41:55,110
You looked like you really didn't want to go.

590
00:41:55,677 --> 00:41:56,242
That's right.

591
00:41:56,242 --> 00:41:57,980
I didn't want to come.

592
00:41:57,980 --> 00:42:00,410
If that's all, I'm going to go eat now.

593
00:42:00,877 --> 00:42:02,410
Hey, why the rush?

594
00:42:06,044 --> 00:42:06,862
Well...

595
00:42:08,445 --> 00:42:10,385
I met a guy this morning.

596
00:42:10,385 --> 00:42:12,904
I heard he was going to the temple,
so I asked to tag along.

597
00:42:13,810 --> 00:42:14,610
Huh?

598
00:42:15,410 --> 00:42:16,750
And after we finished praying...

599
00:42:17,428 --> 00:42:18,790
he invited me to eat.

600
00:42:19,513 --> 00:42:21,034
I'm waiting to eat with him now.

601
00:42:21,644 --> 00:42:22,711
Invited you to eat?

602
00:42:23,254 --> 00:42:23,954
Is he hot?

603
00:42:24,723 --> 00:42:25,809
Is he hitting on you?

604
00:42:27,944 --> 00:42:29,760
No, he wasn't hitting on me.

605
00:42:30,393 --> 00:42:31,612
But he's cute.

606
00:42:32,290 --> 00:42:33,197
He's got that...

607
00:42:33,559 --> 00:42:34,372
organic vibe.

608
00:42:34,553 --> 00:42:37,006
He looks so wholesome, and his style is sick.

609
00:42:37,810 --> 00:42:39,155
Organic is good for you.

610
00:42:39,155 --> 00:42:40,720
It's healthy.

611
00:42:40,901 --> 00:42:43,025
But I'm afraid he might not be so organic.

612
00:42:43,710 --> 00:42:46,277
Excuse me, am I supposed to eat him or something?

613
00:42:46,910 --> 00:42:49,944
After all that praise, you're not going for it?

614
00:42:50,444 --> 00:42:53,877
Yeah, I'm not. But he's the one who's not into me.

615
00:42:54,810 --> 00:42:56,510
What if he was into you?

616
00:42:58,810 --> 00:43:01,910
If he's not wild and fierce, I'll pass.

617
00:43:02,510 --> 00:43:06,144
Yeah, I hope you get railed, sis! Hard and brutal!

618
00:43:07,844 --> 00:43:08,428
Get what?

619
00:43:09,151 --> 00:43:09,960
Get...

620
00:43:12,844 --> 00:43:14,810
You don't have to be so blunt.

621
00:43:15,410 --> 00:43:17,544
Ugh, talking to you is driving me nuts.

622
00:43:18,044 --> 00:43:20,844
I'm not sure if I'm talking to a bar owner
or a mamasan.

623
00:43:21,277 --> 00:43:22,944
That's enough. My boss is looking.

624
00:43:23,310 --> 00:43:24,277
Check your Facebook.

625
00:43:29,944 --> 00:43:30,944
Today is Thursday.

626
00:43:31,810 --> 00:43:33,077
The lucky color is blue.

627
00:43:33,744 --> 00:43:35,010
The unlucky color is black.

628
00:43:38,344 --> 00:43:39,844
I'm wearing the unlucky color.

629
00:43:39,944 --> 00:43:41,877
And my friend just called me a mama-san.

630
00:43:41,877 --> 00:43:42,677
My life is just peachy.

631
00:43:43,610 --> 00:43:44,010
Huh?

632
00:43:44,010 --> 00:43:46,344
Is Aramboy really into all that superstitious stuff now?

633
00:44:00,944 --> 00:44:03,146
I have to give it to you for that album name.

634
00:44:03,146 --> 00:44:04,796
Even though I'm wearing an unlucky color...

635
00:44:05,248 --> 00:44:06,046
this thing here...

636
00:44:06,982 --> 00:44:07,957
is authentic.

637
00:44:08,545 --> 00:44:10,249
Thirteen thousand.

638
00:44:10,610 --> 00:44:11,854
Thirteen thousand?

639
00:44:12,071 --> 00:44:15,377
But if the color isn't compatible with you,
it won't bring you luck.

640
00:44:16,277 --> 00:44:17,192
Whatever you said.

641
00:44:17,463 --> 00:44:18,545
Seriously?

642
00:44:18,726 --> 00:44:20,125
About the shirt color?

643
00:44:32,477 --> 00:44:33,277
Brother.

644
00:44:34,044 --> 00:44:34,844
Where are you going?

645
00:44:36,444 --> 00:44:37,877
To pay for Erng.

646
00:44:40,844 --> 00:44:42,310
Brother, are you really treating me?

647
00:44:43,844 --> 00:44:44,644
Yes.

648
00:44:50,910 --> 00:44:52,044
Go wait upstairs.

649
00:45:01,010 --> 00:45:02,744
When he said "yes" and winked...

650
00:45:03,744 --> 00:45:05,477
my heart just about melted.

651
00:45:18,844 --> 00:45:20,210
Why are you looking at me like that?

652
00:45:21,810 --> 00:45:23,110
I'm craving tea and chicken.

653
00:45:23,844 --> 00:45:25,344
I usually just have liquor and beer.

654
00:45:27,610 --> 00:45:28,944
Let me try some of that tea.

655
00:45:29,810 --> 00:45:31,544
I bet this tea is sweet.

656
00:45:44,344 --> 00:45:45,144
Hmm?

657
00:45:46,544 --> 00:45:47,344
It really is sweet.

658
00:45:47,877 --> 00:45:50,077
Buy tea today and get a free side of diabetes.

659
00:45:53,910 --> 00:45:55,444
I don't usually like sweet things.

660
00:45:57,910 --> 00:45:58,740
I think...

661
00:45:59,283 --> 00:46:00,410
You and I, Brother...

662
00:46:00,681 --> 00:46:02,432
we're definitely not the sweet type.

663
00:46:04,277 --> 00:46:05,077
I guess so.

664
00:46:06,477 --> 00:46:07,397
But I think...

665
00:46:08,682 --> 00:46:09,967
I'll just try the chicken.

666
00:46:12,244 --> 00:46:13,819
I picked the spicy kind for you.

667
00:46:14,226 --> 00:46:15,647
I heard you're good with spicy food.

668
00:46:16,054 --> 00:46:17,841
I love it. Spicy.

669
00:46:18,564 --> 00:46:20,279
Spicy chicken, I love it.

670
00:46:28,010 --> 00:46:28,810
How is it?

671
00:46:29,744 --> 00:46:31,910
This reminds me of Hat Yai fried chicken.

672
00:46:32,077 --> 00:46:32,726
With sticky rice too?

673
00:46:33,178 --> 00:46:33,737
Do you have any?

674
00:46:33,737 --> 00:46:34,344
Yes.

675
00:46:38,610 --> 00:46:39,944
You've got a big appetite.

676
00:46:40,510 --> 00:46:41,310
A lot.

677
00:46:41,677 --> 00:46:42,477
I get hungry often.

678
00:46:44,077 --> 00:46:45,244
Let me know when you're full.

679
00:46:46,077 --> 00:46:47,444
So I can take you for a walk.

680
00:46:57,510 --> 00:46:59,210
Jatukham, the monk's bag edition.

681
00:47:00,144 --> 00:47:02,952
But I don't think it lost its power
because of other people.

682
00:47:02,952 --> 00:47:04,044
It lost its power because of you, Brother.

683
00:47:04,244 --> 00:47:07,077
I was just swinging it around.
It doesn't lose its power that easily.

684
00:47:07,810 --> 00:47:08,610
Right?

685
00:47:12,344 --> 00:47:13,144
Want some?

686
00:47:21,244 --> 00:47:22,410
(Next Episode)
If you were with me...

687
00:47:23,077 --> 00:47:24,010
we wouldn't have to have kids.

688
00:47:24,477 --> 00:47:26,910
Just being Uncle In and Auntie Erng
until we're old is enough.

689
00:47:27,277 --> 00:47:28,077
Okay.

690
00:47:28,877 --> 00:47:29,677
Mom.

691
00:47:30,144 --> 00:47:31,410
In In is here.

692
00:47:31,844 --> 00:47:32,910
I brought him too.

693
00:47:33,810 --> 00:47:34,710
So awesome.

694
00:47:35,744 --> 00:47:36,744
Your mom is lovely.

695
00:47:38,110 --> 00:47:39,244
Ong is such a smartass.

696
00:47:39,744 --> 00:47:41,744
And the super cool Brother Araya.

697
00:47:43,544 --> 00:47:44,344
Sit here for now.

698
00:47:48,052 --> 00:47:48,668
Brother.
